---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
	<section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About the Conference</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="grid-layout">
                <main>
                    <h2>Conference 2026</h2>
                    <p>
                   100 Years of Stafford BeerIn 2026, Metaphorum is inviting you to celebrate with us the centenary of the birth of Stafford Beer, one of the most influential figures in Cybernetics and Systems Thinking. More than fifty years after his invention of the Viable System Model and Team Syntegrity, Beer’s work remains urgently relevant as organisations and societies confront escalating complexity, ecological limits, technological disruption, and crises of governance.
Metaphorum 2026 invites the global cyber-systemic community to reflect, reconnect, and reimagine organisational cybernetics through three interwoven themes
</p>

                    <h2>Who We Are Inviting</h2>
                    <p>We welcome:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Relatives and collaborators</strong> who knew Stafford personally and will share insights into his life and character.</li>
                        <li><strong>Researchers</strong> advancing his legacy by adapting his original thinking and developing innovative cybersystemic methodologies.</li>
                        <li><strong>Consultants and practitioners</strong> who continue to evolve his theories through creative and impactful applications.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Conference Steering Committee</h2>
                    <ul class="committee-list">
                        <li>Angela Espinosa</li>
                        <li>Jon Walker</li>
                        <li>Ayham Fattoum</li>
                        <li>Juliana Alves</li>
                        <li>Camilo Osejo</li>
                        <li>Stephen Harwood</li>
                        <li>Iffat Sabir</li>
                        <li>Andrea Martinez </li>
                        <li>Pedro Pablo Cardoso </li>

                    </ul>
                </main>
                
                <aside>
                    <div class="info-box">
                        <h3>Pre-Conference Events</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>One of the keynotes at ST&SP Conference:</strong> 24–26 March 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Special Stream at ISSS:</strong> June 2026.</li>
                            <li><a href="https://events.asc-cybernetics.org/2026/"><strong>Special Stream at ASC (Brazil):</strong> </a> 3-7 August 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Keynote speaker at ORS (Nottingham):</strong> Sept 8th-10th 2026.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-header {
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
        padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .grid-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    ul {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .committee-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .info-box {
        background: var(--color-background-alt);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    }

    .info-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .info-box ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .info-box li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
